<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/392660-which-translation-shall-i-read-then">Which translation shall I read then?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_392660'><a id="like_count_community_question_392660" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/392660?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">17 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F45974.The_Book_of_Disquiet">like</a></span>

